parameters.name: EnableDeleteTag
parameters.description: Specifies whether to enable lifecycle management for the artifact.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the Container Registry Enterprise Edition instance.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Maximum value: 100. If you specify a value greater than 100 for this parameter, the system reports a parameter error or uses 100 as the maximum value.
